                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Article 10 provides that that extension cannot be made unless made by unanimous agreement. Does that not mean that one nation—say, Iceland or Luxembourg—can bar the entrance of either Soviet Russia or any other country?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f4f97e35-8f34-4943-b200-4e71eba59116" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-05-12/debates/2ee6ff75-6f9e-4fb7-b751-a3fb79cd6b69/NorthAtlanticTreaty#contribution-f4f97e35-8f34-4943-b200-4e71eba59116">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-b1d595f7-a3dd-498a-b972-595a75f8e90d">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-b1d595f7-a3dd-498a-b972-595a75f8e90d">
