            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-4a4fea7e-76ae-47ab-92cd-8e68f1767cbd">
                Mr. Gallacher  (Fife, West)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-4a4fea7e-76ae-47ab-92cd-8e68f1767cbd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
