        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-60df8ea2-c2b6-4410-ac08-c261f31fb3fe">
                Mr. Nutting
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-60df8ea2-c2b6-4410-ac08-c261f31fb3fe" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-05-12/debates/2ee6ff75-6f9e-4fb7-b751-a3fb79cd6b69/NorthAtlanticTreaty#contribution-60df8ea2-c2b6-4410-ac08-c261f31fb3fe">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I really cannot let the hon. Gentleman get away with that. Perhaps his previous frequent interruptions have exhausted him so much that he was asleep during that part of my speech. If the hon. Gentleman had been awake and listening, he would have heard that I clearly said that the Americans should be asked—and discussions should take place forthwith—to underwrite our rearmament programme and the rearmament programmes of the other signatories to the Atlantic Pact.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-60df8ea2-c2b6-4410-ac08-c261f31fb3fe" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
