                Mr. P. Noel-Baker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a91c8e3c-6a26-4142-9d64-6e2a9b24a3a1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-05-12/debates/2ee6ff75-6f9e-4fb7-b751-a3fb79cd6b69/NorthAtlanticTreaty#contribution-a91c8e3c-6a26-4142-9d64-6e2a9b24a3a1">
