                Mr. Gallacher
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-af7a0e83-b9bf-434c-b4b4-a123c9879833" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
