<p class="">What I did say was that I could not see how they could avoid regarding it in that light.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7feca308-32fe-49f6-8c2e-4bb89dc079de" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-05-12/debates/2ee6ff75-6f9e-4fb7-b751-a3fb79cd6b69/NorthAtlanticTreaty#contribution-7feca308-32fe-49f6-8c2e-4bb89dc079de">
